Discrimination for Exercising Privacy Rights
Indeterminate Realms LLC values your privacy and supports your rights to control your personal
information. We affirm that you will not be subject to discriminatory treatment for exercising your
privacy rights. Specifically, if you choose to exercise your rights under the CCPA or any other
privacy legislation, we will not:
l
Deny you goods or services.
